<title>USA: PECO Energy to buy back up to 5 mln shrs.</title>
<headline>PECO Energy to buy back up to 5 mln shrs.</headline>
<dateline>PHILADELPHIA 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>PECO Energy Co's board of directors has authorized the repurchase of up to five million shares of its common stock, the company said Tuesday.</p>
<p>PECO, a public utility company, reported average shares totalling 222.5 million shares in March.</p>
